Private Notes:
The main problem I had was that it's never explained why solar power (or anything else other than coal) is not used.
The author said this was a deliberate stylistic choice (and I agree it worked quite well to create a certain aesthetic). If this was said in a foreword or lampshaded in the book this might have been 5 stars.
